# Title

Multiple Network Attachments with bridge CNI and kubernetes-nmstate

# Abstract

Explain what the session will be about, what will be covered, what will be the
benefits of attending it / what can attendees expect to get from it).

Over the last years the KubeVirt project has improved a lot regarding secondary interfaces networking configuration.
This session will show an end to end configuration from host networking to a VM using just the Kubernetes API with special Custom Resource Definitions.
After the sessions attendees will be able to conect VMs to secondary nics at nodes just using CDRs, without accessing the nodes.

